Changeling With ever-changing appearances, Changelings reside in many societies undetected. Each Changeling can supernaturally adopt any face they like. For some Changelings, a new face is only a disguise. For other Changelings, a new face may reveal an aspect of their soul. Shapechanger Shapechanger - Generic Shapechanger - ACT 1 Shapechanger - ACT 2 Shapechanger - ACT 3 As an action, you can change your appearance. You must adopt a shape that has the same basic arrangement of limbs that you have. Your clothing and equipment aren’t changed by this trait. You learn more shapes upon reaching level 2, 7 and 10 respectively. Fey Ancestry You have <LSTag Tooltip="Advantage">Advantage</LSTag> on <LSTag Tooltip="SavingThrow">Saving Throws</LSTag> against being Charmed, and magic can't put you to sleep. Immunities Turn Back to your unaltered shape. Shapechange into a Humanoid shape from a generic pool of races until you die or use an action to dismiss the effect. You learn more shapes upon reaching level 2, 7 and 10 respectively. Shapechange into a Humanoid shape from ACT 1 until you die or use an action to dismiss the effect. Becomes available upon reaching level 2. Shapechange into a Humanoid shape from ACT 2 until you die or use an action to dismiss the effect. Becomes available upon reaching level 7. Shapechange into a Humanoid shape from ACT 3 until you die or use an action to dismiss the effect. Becomes available upon reaching level 10.
Changeling Instincts Thanks to your connection to the fey realm, you gain <LSTag Tooltip="Proficiency">Proficiency</LSTag> with two of the following <LSTag Tooltip="Skill">Skills</LSTag> of your choice: Deception, Insight, Intimidation, Performance or Persuasion.
